EXIST? FASTGRAF NOT ?\ INCLUDE FGDRIVER.FTH

ONLY FORTH ALSO FASTGRAF ALSO
FORTH DEFINITIONS
DECIMAL

VARIABLE OLDMODE
VARIABLE NEWMODE
VARIABLE MAXX
VARIABLE MAXY
VARIABLE MIDX
VARIABLE MIDY

: FGDEMO19 ( --- )
   FASTGRAPH?
   IF
      FGGETMODE OLDMODE !
      FGAUTOMODE NEWMODE !
