      FGGETMAXX MAXX !
      FGGETMAXY MAXY !
      MAXX @ 2/ MIDX !
      MAXY @ 2/ MIDY !
      15 FGSETCOLOR
      MIDX @ 0 FGMOVE
      MIDX @ MAXY @ 13107 FGDASH
      0 MIDY @ FGMOVE
      MAXX @ MIDY @ 13107 FGDASH
      " D‚monstration de FastGraph (Appuyez sur une touche)" FGTEXT
      FGWAITKEY
      OLDMODE @ FGSETMODE
      FGRESET
      1 FGCURSOR
   ELSE
      CR ." Le driver FastGraph n'est pas charg‚ !!" CR
   THEN
;

EOF

